- Differentialformen: wedge_product, exterior_derivative, hodge_star, lie_derivative_vector
- Einstein-Tensor: G_{ij} = R_{ij} - ½ g_{ij} R
- Schwarzschild-Metrik: ds² = -(1-r_s/r)c²dt² + (1-r_s/r)⁻¹ dr²
- Vakuum-Check: check_vacuum_solution (G_{ij} ≈ 0?)
